

GIT WORKTREES
    
    SETUP

        cd /hdd_r6/gcox/git/llvm-project/
        git worktree add /hdd_r6/gcox/src/llvm-project/9.0.0 llvmorg9.0.0
        git worktree add /hdd_r6/gcox/src/llvm-project/master remotes/origin/master 


DIRECTORY LAYOUT

    git/
       cloned git repositories 

    obj/
        object files and build results

    pub/
        "install" directory

    src/
        git worktrees -- what the compiler readd

    tmp/
        temporary junk and detritus


WORK FLOW



NOTES

    libcxxabi is the lower-level library


SEQUENCE

    bin/build-000-bootstrap
        tools /opt/llvm-9.0.0
        enable projects llvm clang
        enable runtimes compiler-rt libcxxabi libcxx
        install to stage-100-target

    bin/build-100-bootstrap
        tools stage-100-target
        enable projects llvm clang compiler-rt libcxxabi libcxx
        install to stage-200-target

    bin/build-200-bootstrap
        tools stage-100-target
        enable projects clang;clang-tools-extra;libcxx;libcxxabi;compiler-rt;libunwind;lld;lldb;llvm;openmp
        install to stage-200-target

